{
  "annotations": [
    {
      "start_time": 0,
      "end_time": 7,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "As a group, immigrant workers are rarely seen and seldom heard in modern U.S. media."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Maria Hinojosa",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "261545e8-fc21-4e07-981c-02bf8d3fda6f"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 7,
      "end_time": 11,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Beginning June 1st, though, Bread and Roses will be released nationwide."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Maria Hinojosa",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Year 2000",
          "category": "Time Period"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "7aa111b4-1954-4612-8fcd-8ed762847da8"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 11,
      "end_time": 18,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The bilingual film chronicles the struggle of immigrants to form a union in Southern California during the 1990s."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Maria Hinojosa",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Southern California",
          "category": "Geographic"
        },
        {
          "tag": "The 1990s",
          "category": "Time Period"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Film",
          "category": "Artistic Medium"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "287992c6-b4f6-4e63-8d34-21616d4e3f88"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 18,
      "end_time": 20,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The film premiered recently in Los Angeles."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Maria Hinojosa",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "71a50955-d0f2-48d1-bf0a-a7a0712e67c7"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 20,
      "end_time": 24,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Correspondent Robin Yorovich was there and filed this report."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Maria Hinojosa",
          "category": "Speaker"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "45c00021-be28-418a-bdea-8a209dc36b27"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 24,
      "end_time": 31,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "As Bread and Roses opens, its heroine, Maya Montenegro, played by Pilar Padilla, survives a dramatic border crossing."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Pilar Padilla",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Excerpt",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "973c6f0d-e7cb-4135-8ddc-96694f95f28b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 43,
      "end_time": 50,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Once in Los Angeles, she joins her sister, Rosa, played by Elpidia Carrillo, working as a janitor in a downtown high-rise. Soon, a union organizer comes calling."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Elpidia Carrillo",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "e51fd7f7-f9b5-49d3-bb88-cceac720353b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 52,
      "end_time": 59,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": " Hi, is Rosa in? Yeah, Hold On. Mami! Que? Hay alguien en la puerta- "
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Pilar Padilla",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Elpidia Carrillo",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Excerpt",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "a129dd76-1224-49d0-a9d5-4d6268130107"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 59,
      "end_time": 67,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Hi, I'm Sam Shapiro, the Justice for Janitors campaign."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Adrien Brody",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Excerpt",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "2f19ff24-03bd-4d86-aadf-2218701e76f7"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 67,
      "end_time": 70,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "I'm Rosa, Justice for Rosa's campaign."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Elpidia Carrillo",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Excerpt",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "924850aa-bb49-4ba7-8b2d-eb69ccc09346"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 70,
      "end_time": 79,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Maya liked Sam, played by actor Adrien Brody and the idea of the union, but the more hardened and cynical Rosa is not so easily persuaded."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Adrien Brody",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "4c6b57b6-00b1-4ae6-8e25-673b18e73cbc"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 79,
      "end_time": 84,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "There is every chance you can get fired. I've seen it before. What are you going to do? Pay the rent? Feed my kids?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Excerpt",
          "category": "Sounds"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Elpidia Carrillo",
          "category": "Names"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "80e327ab-3745-4be7-9e42-99f9be984305"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 84,
      "end_time": 88,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "And you? You better keep away from this nice one. Listen, they will fire anyway! "
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Excerpt",
          "category": "Sounds"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Elpidia Carrillo",
          "category": "Names"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "6d6fd844-3718-4b4c-bdba-527e6e683e8f"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 89,
      "end_time": 98,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Nearly a decade after he came up with the idea for Bread and Roses, screenwriter Paul Laverty was back in Los Angeles for the film's opening party."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Paul Laverty",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "403b9d69-9129-4430-8230-6a0fee97e578"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 98,
      "end_time": 108,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "He'd just arrived from his state of Scotland in the early 90s when thousands of janitors, mostly from Mexico and Central America, were beginning to demand better pay and benefits."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Paul Laverty",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "179f49d3-37fb-4cef-8e87-1f3e6aedc584"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 109,
      "end_time": 114,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "I went along and I met the people. I met cleaners who were activists and trade union organizers."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Paul Laverty",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "5c1be10a-8cbf-40ab-814a-b2831cd71190"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 114,
      "end_time": 125,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "And they were fantastic people. And there was a kind of a spark to them that really got to me, you know, the way they organized and a real depth of human experience."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Paul Laverty",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "b019a926-9839-43ce-85bb-bd7262d28f43"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 125,
      "end_time": 130,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "You know, and there was a determination to organize and change their lives without making a fuss or playing victim."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Paul Laverty",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "bd486165-30d1-48db-a9a7-90aca91cce56"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 130,
      "end_time": 139,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Laverty convinced director Ken Loach there was a film in the story of the janitors and he began poking around the union where he ran into organizer Jono Shaffer."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Film",
          "category": "Artistic Medium"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Ken Loach",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "1fb1bcf8-ddf5-4334-95f0-b8be4c454fbb"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 139,
      "end_time": 147,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The first time I met Paul, he sort of appeared and started asking a bunch of questions and I was totally suspicious about who this guy was, you know."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Jono Shaffer",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "7d6007d6-0125-49cf-8dbe-b8d4e7282b5d"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 147,
      "end_time": 157,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "But over time he, you know, sort of wore on me. He said he was making a movie. I was like, yeah, right, everybody in L.A. is going to make a movie. You know, it's like this will end up in some trash can somewhere."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Jono Shaffer",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Angeles",
          "category": "Geographic"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Film",
          "category": "Artistic Medium"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "41fcfaff-7ab9-4748-a485-8ad77614c38b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 157,
      "end_time": 168,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Shaffer, who bears a resemblance to the film's organizer, says Laverty and Ken Loach took some artistic license, making the work of the organizer a little more reckless and spontaneous than it is in real life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Film",
          "category": "Artistic Medium"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Jono Shaffer",
          "category": "Speaker"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "d12d8f85-0b2a-45dc-9dd5-8953f69365aa"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 168,
      "end_time": 174,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "But he says they didn't exaggerate the difficulty of organizing a union in the United States."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Film",
          "category": "Artistic Medium"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "193eea81-990b-40b2-a9e4-eea5e10f637c"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 174,
      "end_time": 180,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Real life janitor Dolores Sanchez says she saw a lot of herself and her co-workers in Bread and Roses."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Film",
          "category": "Artistic Medium"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "f2789338-7848-4b40-9a78-b06965241dcd"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 181,
      "end_time": 190,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "I don't know. I cried during the whole movie because it does have several things that those of us from other countries have been through."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Dolores Sanchez",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "03fa202a-02e2-44a5-b41c-2f4df33e5a59"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 190,
      "end_time": 200,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "For the three and a half years it took to organize the union at her company, Sanchez says she went to work every night fighting her fears of a confrontation with the boss or of losing her job."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "d5989e56-e112-4f19-be63-c357218e23f6"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 200,
      "end_time": 208,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "During the three and a half years, I'd ask myself, if you lose your job, how are you going to support your kids?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Dolores Sanchez",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "182e738f-86f4-4c31-83fb-be9b7a927061"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 208,
      "end_time": 219,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Now Sanchez says the sacrifices of those years are paying off. She couldn't have a much wanted third child until she got family health insurance. Now she's got it and her baby's due late this summer."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Labor Organizing",
          "category": "Subject"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "ab014ff8-b375-475a-bfc6-731da233f0af"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 219,
      "end_time": 223,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Bread and Roses mixes drama and fiction with reality."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "0248ca34-91e0-4cd2-95d4-56fda011514b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 223,
      "end_time": 232,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Director Ken Loach required the actors to work a shift alongside real life janitors, some of whom also appear in the movie along with other L.A. activists."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Bread and Roses",
          "category": "Work Titles"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Ken Loach",
          "category": "Names"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "55b9d694-f7e7-40ce-adff-2189be390381"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 232,
      "end_time": 239,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Si se puede, si se puede, si se puede..."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Los Jornaleros del Norte",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Music",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "6a257a98-6f42-44aa-a3cf-e4d2b6081e8c"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 239,
      "end_time": 249,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "In this scene at a union celebration, the music is provided by Los Jornaleros del Norte, five men who haven't quit their real life day jobs."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Jornaleros del Norte",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Music",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "cdc95936-610e-4e97-b133-8e957a36431c"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 249,
      "end_time": 255,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "They're members of L.A.'s day laborers union and they play their topical songs at labor and immigrant rights events."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Robin Yurovich",
          "category": "Speaker"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Los Jornaleros del Norte",
          "category": "Names"
        },
        {
          "tag": "Music",
          "category": "Sounds"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "bddc6064-6b25-48f3-9486-eb9d6fc5c0e6"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 255,
      "end_time": 265,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Bread and Roses has received mostly thumbs up from the critics, but as a business venture, it's a little risky, says its distributor Tom Ortenberg of Lionsgate Films."
            }
          ]
        }
